title: net/http: Typo in Documentation
body:
What did you do? Read the documentation
What did you expect to see? The word "directory"
What did you see instead? The word "direcory"

https://github.com/golang/go/blob/b04f3b06ec347543b0eafe82dcfb0e05885d3feb/src/net/http/fs.go#L454
https://golang.org/pkg/net/http/#ServeFile
